Food coupons, bicycles, open-air films have rekindled the memories of the Chinese in the 1980s. At that time, Chinese people were striving for a "Xiaokang family." Now, China has accomplished the building of a moderately prosperous society in all respects. So let's embark on a trip down memory lane through this old diary. Credits: Designer: Yuan Xin Animator: Chen Hangyu Senior producer: Wei Wei Managing director: Mei Yan (To submit cartoons and share story ideas or feedback on our cartoon page, please contact us at cartoon_opinions@cgtn.com)